markets.title: Will Yale drop in national university rankings?
markets.rules_primary: If Yale drops in the rankings, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: All that matters is the rank associated with the college/university -- even if a single university goes from being alone in first place to being tied for first place, that is not a drop in ranking. The 2026 Best National University Rankings are expected to be released in September 2025.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
